<div id="pf54eb" class="pf w57 h359" data-page-no="54eb"><div class="pc pc54eb w57 h359"><div class="t md0d x71 h87 y11ed ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">96 </div><div class="t m86e x85 h5a y1bcd ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Every member: </div><div class="t m311 x5e h5a y1bce ff1 fs6 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">praying . . giving . </div><div class="t m685 x61 h27 y3005 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">proclaim the resurrection with such confidence, power, and effective-</div><div class="t m318 x64 h27 y2feb ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ness! If they had known the story to be a lie, why would so many of </div><div class="t ma9 x61 h27 y2bc7 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them have been willing to lay down their lives for their faith? </div><div class="t m370 x26 h87 y2b31 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">13. Why can we witness for Christ with confidence and courage, </div><div class="t m1369 x4e h87 y2977 ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">whatever our circumstances? Matt. 28:18, 20; compare Acts 4:31. </div><div class="t mcae x26 h87 y22fd ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">AM I REJOICING IN CHRIST&apos;S DEATH AND RESURRECTION? </div><div class="t m34e x61 h27 y2379 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t mb85 x63 h27 y2379 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">What has happened in my life as I have accepted the truth of </div><div class="t m7f1 x61 h27 y233f ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ&apos;s death and resurrection? </div><div class="t m34e x61 h27 y20ea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">• </div><div class="t m14bb x66 h27 y20ea ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Am I eager to share my knowledge of Christ with others? What </div><div class="t md7 x64 h27 y2080 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">positive experiences have I had as I have shared my faith in His death </div><div class="t m46b x61 h27 y11d5 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and resurrection? </div><div class="t m663 x26 h87 y12ec ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">FURTHER STUDY AND MEDITATION: </div><div class="t mdb7 xac h27 y12ec ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Read &quot;In Pilate&apos;s Judgment </div><div class="t m326 x26 h27 y1953 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Hall,&quot; &quot; &apos;It Is Finished,&apos; &quot; &quot; &apos;The Lord Is Risen,&apos; &quot; and &quot;Go Teach All </div><div class="t m63b x26 h27 y1955 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Nations,&quot; chapters 77, 79, 81, and 86 in </div><div class="t m3f7 x4b h16 y1955 ff6 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Desire of Ages, </div><div class="t m13b1 xcd h27 y1955 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">pp. 723-740, </div><div class="t m15c1 x26 h27 y1956 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">758-768, 779-787, and 818-828. </div><div class="t mbc7 x26 h87 y187a ff1 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">SUMMARY: </div><div class="t m209 x6c h27 y187a ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The mistreatment, death, and resurrection of Christ reveal as </div><div class="t m26e x26 h27 y19b2 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">nothing else can how much God cares for sinners. No earthly king would </div><div class="t mbb2 x26 h27 y1ff6 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ever act as Jesus did while possessing the power to break the bonds of </div><div class="t m488 x26 h27 y1e60 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">death. When Jesus died Satan&apos;s kingdom was defeated. The penalty for the </div><div class="t m1bb7 x26 h27 y18ee ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sins of humanity was paid, and our redemption was assured. Jesus rose as </div><div class="t m432 x26 h27 y1f69 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">recognized King of the universe and returned to heaven to apply for us the </div><div class="t m114c x26 h27 y17b3 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">blessings of His sacrifice. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
